name: alberti view
description:
The accommodation is located in the famous square, located on the third and last floor without an elevator, of a building from the early 1900s.
Very bright and airy, you have a beautiful view of the
dome of Brunelleschi, evocative is the view during
sunrise and sunset.
Very comfortable is the availability of an indoor garage
(for a fee) ALBERTI PARKING
there are also plenty of businesses
such as bakeries, bars, pharmacies, restaurants, etc.
Downtown is a 15 min walk

name: Relax and charme in Santa Maria Novella
description:
Enjoy a stylish vacation at this centrally located apartment. Entirely renovated, within walking distance of Santa Maria Novella Central Station and major museums and monuments. You will be at ease in a stylish and comfortable environment. Wi-Fi air conditioning microwave and traditional oven, toaster.
First floor with easy stairs, seating area. You will stay 400m from the Basilica of Santa Maria Novella and 600m from the city center. Ponte Vecchio is 1 km away.

name: Casa degli Aliotti
description:
Casa degli Aliotti is an apartment on the first floor of a building from the early 1400s.
Within its walls are therefore typical and original elements of the classic Florentine style.
Its location is very convenient, which allows you to enjoy the wonders of the historic center, on foot, and at the same time full of services of all kinds. There are two double bedrooms, a living area, a well-equipped kitchen and an outdoor area for exclusive use.
